Description:
    Creates a gulpfile (and a package.json file if required).

Example:
    yo gulp-b

    This will create:
        gulpfile.js
	package.json (if there is no package.json file)

    yo gulp-b:sass

    This will update:
        gulpfile.js with a sass task to compile scss files.
	package.json to include gulp-sass

    yo gulp-b:browsersync

    This will update;
        gulpfile.js with a browsersync task to watch files and reload the browser.
	package.json to include browser-sync.

    yo gulp-b:rollup

    This will create:
        rollup.config.js

    This will update:
        gulpfile.js with a rollup task to

	package.json to include the following packages:
  	    vinyl-source-stream
	    vinyl-buffer
	    rollup-plugin-node-resolve
	    rollup-plugin-commonjs
	    rollup-stream 
	    rollup-plugin-postcss


	    


